{"tid":2041010,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「不做真相仲裁者」朱克伯格拒干預","createTime":"2020-05-29T03:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T04:40:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2a6e6879f6fb3641f5823857217830ea9b35a59a","tid":2041010,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:17:01.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200529/4ZF7KYTJMGMU3CW4PJQS6H5O64/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200529%2F4ZF7KYTJMGMU3CW4PJQS6H5O64%2F&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33HpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=27480120\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200529%2F4ZF7KYTJMGMU3CW4PJQS6H5O64%2F&h=99e24235\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200529/4ZF7KYTJMGMU3CW4PJQS6H5O64/</a><br />\n<br />\n「不做真相仲裁者」朱克伯格拒干預<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/D5T34XVM5IVJ3VJXA2UAX35M4Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FD5T34XVM5IVJ3VJXA2UAX35M4Q.jpg&h=60b5b840&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱克伯格<br />\n<br />\n社交媒體巨擘facebook行政總裁朱克伯格批評Twitter不應該為美國總統特朗普兩條推文加上查明事實的標註，並指私人公司不應擔當「真相的仲裁者」。<br />\n<br />\n對於Twitter首次在特朗普推文下加入連結，指「特朗普毫無根據地稱郵寄選票會導致選民欺詐」。朱克伯格接受霍士新聞台記者佩里諾的訪問時說，「我們就這事擁有與Twitter不同的政策。我強烈地相信fb不應該為人們在網上的所有言論，擔當真相的仲裁者。整體來說，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTwitter：連結矛盾陳述<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：社交網打假兩難：不理捱轟 干預受壓<br />\n<br />\nTwitter行政總裁多爾西就推文指，平台在推文加入標註「不代表我們擔當了『真相的仲裁者』」，此舉的目的是要把「互相矛盾的陳述連結起來，顯示持不一樣觀點的資訊，讓人們自行判斷」。多家社交媒體巨擘就應否審查政治言論的真偽有過多番爭論，fb去年起採取不干預態度；Twitter則停登政治廣告，今個月起更為具事實爭議的推文，貼上請用戶查明事實的提示。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n英國《泰晤士報》"},{"pid":"8e461e41cbf9832d1bdacee8d127d96c29d0e3c0","tid":2041010,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d462d74dd0cb3ab28b8b702d3048e9488e7d3588","tid":2041010,"uid":62151,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:21:14.000Z","msg":"講政治審查twitter同FB比連車尾燈都見唔到"},{"pid":"85bc4d3b18cec00ba804ca062db3703166197389","tid":2041010,"uid":31215,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d462d74dd0cb3ab28b8b702d3048e9488e7d3588","tid":2041010,"uid":62151,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:21:14.000Z","msg":"講政治審查twitter同FB比連車尾燈都見唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:23:39.000Z","msg":"講政治審查google 最撚勁<br />\n嚴過tiktok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc124cc2cd7b4b88b3131e17de47604d9f6fe32","tid":2041010,"uid":173179,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:24:31.000Z","msg":"依家兩家轉邊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b730eeb763d2b19f48674e95cbeedbc685b55135","tid":2041010,"uid":45376,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:24:46.000Z","msg":"請撚晒啲支那五毛做言論審查<br />\n緊係做唔到真相仲裁啦冚家剷"},{"pid":"181c5c0e907661c1c9da754ba90fe69bd06028ac","tid":2041010,"uid":41389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:26:48.000Z","msg":"期待美國公司鬥黃"},{"pid":"01de90b9b64e0eedb606121a4127abb4624a9f9a","tid":2041010,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:55:12.000Z","msg":"youtube 頭號PK"},{"pid":"dbae8853d6eccf47fdc5b85ebbbd69ff4618137f","tid":2041010,"uid":245388,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:56:07.000Z","msg":"豬閪八嘎最無資格講"},{"pid":"314293ca1f16f1a9e3aedabc8bb7f1e685964ca4","tid":2041010,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite